data.description: Charming & adorable cottage right in the heart of Historic Madisonville! Take a walk or ride your bike on the newly finished sidewalks to restaurants, coffee shops, the farmers market & the Tchefuncte River. Corner lot features two large gorgeous oak trees on the property. This lovely home has been renovated with all new floors, new cabinets, new custom doors interior and exterior, brand NEW stainless steel appliances (new range, microwave, refrigerator and new washer/dryer ALL included in the sale!) Beautiful bathroom features mosaic tile floors, new vanity, new fixtures and subway tile shower/tub combo. If you love homes with character, are looking to downsize, own rental property or just want to be by everything Madisonville has to offer, this one is for you at an affordable price! Come take a tour and fall in LOVE.
